{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a5ad3f0e-d20e-4312-96f5-60a72fafe093",
    "name": "S4W — API",
    "description": "Integration API for the s4w file store (no admin panel).\n\n## Authorization\n- **Tenant** — instance token in `Authorization: Bearer {{instanceToken}}`. instanceId is taken FROM the token (not passed in the path). The token is created in the admin panel and must be **ACTIVE**.\n- **Public** — no authorization. Only public files (root + public sections): `/o/{instanceId}/...`.\n\n## Getting started\n1. Get an instance token in the panel and put it into `{{instanceToken}}`.\n2. For public links, fill `{{instanceId}}`.\n\n`{{fileId}}` is captured automatically after `Upload file`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "15016352",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/15016352-a5ad3f0e-d20e-4312-96f5-60a72fafe093?source=collection_link"
  },
